{
  "title": "Prologue: Shiina Hiyori's Monologue",
  "content": "<h1 class=\"heading_1\"><a class=\"heading-link\" href=\"/read/y3v3/2\">Prologue:<br/>Shiina Hiyori&apos;s Monologue</a></h1><hr/><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">AS THE SEA breeze brushed against my skin, I recalled that day.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">Under the sunset sky I spent with Ayanokouji-kun, in front of the school building that should&#x2019;ve looked just the same as always.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">To me, that was a wonderful, irreplaceable and vivid memory.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">However, I couldn&apos;t take that one final step.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">&#x2018;<em>I like you</em>&#x2019;&#x2014;in the end, I wasn&#x2019;t able to say those words out loud.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">But I think that was the right thing to do.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">After all, Ayanokouji-kun and I are in different classes... we&#x2019;re enemies.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>If our class is to be defeated in this</em>&#xa0;<em>special exam as well, and the gap is to widen...</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">That will become the final turning point determining whether or not we can reach Class A.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">I&#x2019;ve always known that.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">And for myself, it is a major decision&#x2014;a path I choose with resolve.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">To defeat Ayanokouji-kun.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">To inflict defeat upon Ayanokouji-kun.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>For that purpose... what must I do?</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>What can I do?</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">In this special exam, I see a path to survival and a path to death at the same time.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">However&#x2014;</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">A painful emotion naturally wells up within me.</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\">Gazing out at the vast ocean, all alone, I continue to stare quietly&#x2014;</p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>It seems I am unable to be of use to the class and I will lose this final battle as well.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>I am sorry, Ryuuen-kun.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>I am sorry, Ayanokouji-kun.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>Please forgive me for being so pathetic.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>And please, take care of yourself.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>Please...</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>Even if we&#x2019;re far apart, my feelings will never change.</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>In this world with no one else, all alone&#x2014;</em></p><p class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left\"><em>Until the whistle signaling the end sounds, I will continue to gaze out alone&#x2014;</em></p>",
